,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"玩CC 最唔鐘意agent 女"},{"pid":"2a2987c591b221e1196b9647b64276a1abb7c67a","tid":1896420,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"貝依霖？"},{"pid":"7394166f1f1dbfa7dbe99ab95be0ff48ca53ba9b","tid":1896420,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac0ae662066d64f84361f29055b23c9d3ca2f59e","tid":1896420,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dda7c28f1be109d4e894103aa1b2b649f78dd41","tid":1896420,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a505fb9e9b83b1e956247a3430d6289e399dd4","tid":1896420,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"咁平得唔得㗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"係佢比返你呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388d0dc4f9b640ba6643906442491a01d2f3c3ca","tid":1896420,"uid":2932,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"38a7a41ea2ec9efdfabafd67b3585c411b82622f","tid":1896420,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"有冇見到你啲親戚老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nz11qDV1Iqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fnz11qDV1Iqw&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=bd0d8fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nz11qDV1Iqw</a><br />\n<br />\n後來本刊再聯絡「雞頭」，對方則相約記者到位於尖沙咀的君怡酒店交易，更一度催促記者盡快到場。記者在該酒店發現該援交妹本人，在門外跟她閒聊幾句。援交妹表示不敢站到房門外，因為怕被閉路電視拍攝到，而她亦表示同集團的援交妹們一般12點下班，各人分佈在油尖旺區的不同酒店，在這家酒店開工則是新近之事。記者表明身份，意欲進行訪問，即被援交妹拒絕，她亦隨即關上房門。<br />\n<br />\n其後記者在現場觀察，發現嫖客均戴上口罩。有客人到了房間外面，內心都非常掙扎。有的在門前徘徊、有的低頭玩手機冷靜，有的則決定離去。客人往來不絕，生意非常暢旺。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，援交女KK屬於一個有組織的援交賣淫集團，主要於telegram招攬客人。這個集團除KK之外，旗下還有另外5至6個女仔，聲稱以陀地妹為主，肉金由1600到5000元不等。根據行規，集團會跟援交妹平分肉金。援交集團對旗下的援交妹監督非常嚴謹。我們曾假扮嫖客，約好時間後沒有出現，馬伕便立即到援交妹的房間檢查，以防援交妹私自接客，獨吞肉金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yLDrqxe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyLDrqxe.jpg&h=69609684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad5dd9f5d8d4ea78d98f308e5f63569cc09b2799","tid":1896420,"uid":19676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfd18adfa4919571f527c7234bb51c52d95ca733","tid":1896420,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc41f3703292c427e62a2168913177d6a525946d","tid":1896420,"uid":27482,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"有些嫖客最後都能理智戰勝慾望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"去到門口先淆底咁撚搞笑...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"見到豬閪你仲入去？"},{"pid":"e980fc19bd3d3b72823338b2067258a03af29ec7","tid":1896420,"uid":144024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4469b555ec81015db0a7641e96820f6938a968be","tid":1896420,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca6578b2c63b48fec4c8e7b52744c1755cde338c","tid":1896420,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d73e5d743d46fa717f223009238419d2ccd428","tid":1896420,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfd18adfa